---
title: Chorizo Stuffed Chicken Breast  with roast baby potatoes and caramelised onion gravy
description: As is seen in a lot of Iberian cooking, chicken and chorizo make a classic combination. For good reason! The chorizo stuffing in this recipe adds a slightly smoky flavour to the succulent chicken breast, with breadcrumbs and Italian style cheese for a bit of added bite!
